PDL/Opt/NonLinear version 0.01
=============================

This module provide some optimization routines for PDL.

INSTALLATION

Go to opti_lib directory and edit Makefile to reflect your C and Fortran compiler.
Type make and copy libopti.so to u/usr/local/lib.

After change to root directory and type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires PDL.

